go_data.justification: Alpha-1-Antichymotrypsin is mentioned alongside alpha-1-antitrypsin which blocks SARS-CoV-2 infection by inhibiting the processing of SARS-CoV-2 S protein by furin and TMPRSS2, implying a similar function.
Alpha-1-Antichymotrypsin is enriched in ChipEXOs, which are extracellular vesicles.
